widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>她声称Reddit已“拒绝”回应她的担忧。她写道：“但我不知道这对你们其他人来说也是一个更大的问题。” “我真的很抱歉。”她向粉丝们保证，她“将更加努力地处理”这些帐户。</p><p>过去，马斯克因让亲纳粹的概况在X/Twitter上蓬勃发展，分享右翼模因并看似支持反犹太阴谋论而受到批评。 <a href="https://apnews.com/article/elon-musk-x-antisemitism-twitter-ads-83e68f03e9bf1d261c1a8c55066c4e59" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>每次</em></a>，后者在2023年导致了该平台的广告商出埃及。 </p><figure id="attachment_3830356" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3830356" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3830356" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Elon-Musk-and-Grimes.jpg" alt="Grimes和Elon Musk" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Elon-Musk-and-Grimes.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Elon-Musk-and-Grimes-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Elon-Musk-and-Grimes-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Elon-Musk-and-Grimes-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Elon-Musk-and-Grimes-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Elon-Musk-and-Grimes-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3830356" class="wp-caption-text"> Elon Musk and Grimes在2018年。信贷：Stephen Lovekin/Variety/Penske Media通过Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>他在就职典礼上的手势引发了社交媒体用户的反对，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lamb-of-gods-randy-blythe-brands-elon-musk-a-fucking-asshole-following-nazi-like-gesture-at-trump-inauguration-3831684">上帝的兰迪·布莱斯（Randy Blythe）的羔羊</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/my-chemical-romance-frank-iero-calls-out-elon-musk-controversial-salute-3830992">我的化学浪漫史的弗兰克·艾罗（Frank Iero）</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/snl-star-chloe-fineman-says-she-has-no-regrets-alleging-that-elon-musk-made-her-cry-3831207">《星期六夜现场》（SNL）演员克洛伊·菲尔曼</a>喜剧节目包括与Fineman的交流，据称使她哭泣。</p><