pe的电视之类的电视也为专辑提供了额外的制作和贡献。</p><p>根据新闻稿，“ Thee Black Boltz”是“向Adebimpe倾向于写和唱人类状况的倾向 - 在其所有形式的所有形式下，在其所有压力下，无论大小都很小。” “ Thee Black Boltz”定于4月18日通过Sub Pop发布。您可以<a href="https://prescriptionpr.createsend1.com/t/j-l-wlkdilk-iyuukkjddt-t/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>预订专辑。 </p><figure id="attachment_3832687" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3832687" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3832687" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tunde-Adebimpe-Thee-Black-Boltz-Album-Artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="Tunde Adebimpe“ Thee Black Boltz”专辑艺术品。信用：出版" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tunde-Adebimpe-Thee-Black-Boltz-Album-Artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tunde-Adebimpe-Thee-Black-Boltz-Album-Artwork.-Credit-PRESS-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tunde-Adebimpe-Thee-Black-Boltz-Album-Artwork.-Credit-PRESS-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tunde-Adebimpe-Thee-Black-Boltz-Album-Artwork.-Credit-PRESS-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tunde-Adebimpe-Thee-Black-Boltz-Album-Artwork.-Credit-PRESS-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tunde-Adebimpe-Thee-Black-Boltz-Album-Artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tunde-Adebimpe-Thee-Black-Boltz-Album-Artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3832687" class="wp-caption-text"> Tunde Adebimpe“ Thee Black Boltz”专辑艺术品。信用：出版</figcaption></figure><h3><strong>Tunde Adebimp的“ Thee Thee Black Boltz”曲目列表是：</strong></h3><p> <strong>1。&#39;Thee Black Boltz&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>2。“磁”</strong><br /> <strong>3。&#39;吃了月亮&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>4。&#39;pinstack&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>5。&#39;Drop&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>6。&#39;ily&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>7。“最多”</strong><br /> <strong>8。“上帝知道”</strong><br /> <strong>9。&#39;蓝色&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>10。</strong><br /> <strong>11。</strong></p><p>在其他新闻中，电台上的电视最近被宣布为今年的表演者之一<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/vampire-weekend-rilo-kiley-bloc-party-lead-stacked-just-like-heaven-2025-line-up-3832345">，就像《天堂剧院</a>》和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/new-order-weezer-beach-house-justice-lead-kilby-block-party-2025-line-up-3818440">Killby Block派对2025</a> 。乐队最近结束了他们的复出巡回演唱会，使他们<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-tv-on-the-radio-surprise-intimate-show-new-yorks-tv-eye-reunion-tour-3815730">在纽约的电视眼中进行了一场惊喜表演</a>，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tv-on-the-radio-20th-anniversary-reissue-of-desperate-youth-blood-thirsty-babes-3813226">继续发布了他们的首张专辑《绝望的青年血液渴的宝贝》</a> ，以纪念其20周年。</p><p>在其他地方，阿德比姆（Adebimpe）也被<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tv-on-the-radios-tunde-adebimpe-is-on-the-cast-of-star-wars-skeleton-crew-ive-been-about-it-since-82-3818629">确认为新的《星球大战》系列<em>骨骼工作人员</em>的演员之一。</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tv-on-the-radios-tunde-adebimpe-shares-reflective-drop-and-announces-debut-solo-album-thee-black-boltz-3832680">电台的Tunde Adebimpe上的电视台分享了反思性的“ Drop”，并宣布首张个人专辑“ Thee Black Boltz”</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
